# Defense-in-depth: never accidentally commit per-machine secret files.
# These should live at $HOME, not in the repo — but if a stray copy lands
# in the working tree (e.g. fat-fingered `cp`), keep it out of git.
*.local
!*.local.example
.zshenv.local
zshenv.local

# macOS noise
.DS_Store

# Editor noise
*.swp
*.swo
